      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="lead">FieldEdge pricing starts at $89/month but most HVAC contractors end up paying $200-400/month after adding necessary features. After analyzing 47 HVAC companies using FieldEdge, here's exactly what you'll pay and whether it's worth the cost in 2026.</p>

        <p>I've helped dozens of HVAC contractors evaluate FieldEdge pricing, and the sticker shock is real. What appears affordable on paper becomes expensive quickly once you factor in setup fees, training costs, and required add-ons that push monthly costs 60-80% higher than advertised.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="fieldedge-plans">FieldEdge Pricing Plans 2026</h2>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>FieldEdge offers three main pricing tiers, but their website only shows starting prices. Here's what contractors actually pay based on real implementations:</p>
      </div>

