              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Typical Cost</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Best For</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Essential</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$89/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$150-200/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">1-3 technicians</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Professional</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$149/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$300-450/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">4-10 technicians</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Enterprise</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Custom quote</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$600-1,200/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">10+ technicians</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p><strong>Why the price difference?</strong> FieldEdge's advertised prices assume minimal usage. Real-world implementations require inventory management ($39/month), advanced reporting ($49/month), and additional user licenses that quickly inflate costs.</p>

        <p>One contractor in Atlanta told me: "We started at $149/month for Professional but ended up at $380/month once we added the features we actually needed. The sales rep didn't mention half these costs upfront."</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="implementation-costs">Implementation & Setup Costs</h2>

