        <p>FieldEdge implementation costs are often overlooked but can add $500-1,500 to your first year. Here's the breakdown from 12 recent implementations:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Setup fee:</strong> $299-599 (varies by plan and data complexity)</li>
          <li><strong>Data migration:</strong> $150-400 (depends on previous system)</li>
          <li><strong>Training sessions:</strong> $150/hour (most companies need 4-8 hours)</li>
          <li><strong>Custom integrations:</strong> $500-1,200 (if connecting to existing tools)</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Total implementation costs typically range from $800-2,200 for most HVAC companies. Companies with complex inventory systems or multiple integrations often pay $1,500-3,000.</p>
      </div>

