      <h2 id="hidden-fees">Hidden Fees & Add-Ons That Increase Costs</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>FieldEdge's base pricing excludes features most HVAC companies need. Here are common add-ons that inflate monthly costs:</p>

        <h3>Essential Add-Ons (Most Companies Need These)</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Advanced Reporting:</strong> $49/month (needed for profit analysis)</li>
          <li><strong>Inventory Management:</strong> $39/month (essential for parts tracking)</li>
          <li><strong>Credit Card Processing:</strong> 2.9% + $0.30 per transaction</li>
          <li><strong>Additional Mobile Licenses:</strong> $25/month per extra technician</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Common Integrations</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>QuickBooks Pro:</strong> $25/month</li>
          <li><strong>Marketing integrations:</strong> $35/month each</li>
          <li><strong>Call tracking:</strong> $29/month (or use <a href="https://partners.callrail.com/ut5waejxy35l" rel="sponsored nofollow">CallRail</a> directly)</li>
