      <h2 id="roi-calculator">FieldEdge ROI Calculator</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>To justify FieldEdge's cost, you need to generate additional revenue or save significant time. Here's the ROI breakdown for a 5-technician company:</p>

        <h3>Annual Costs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Software:</strong> $4,080-5,400</li>
          <li><strong>Setup & training:</strong> $800-1,200 (first year)</li>
          <li><strong>Total Year 1:</strong> $4,880-6,600</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Required Benefits to Break Even</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Additional jobs:</strong> 15-20 more service calls per month</li>
          <li><strong>Time savings:</strong> 8-12 hours per week across all staff</li>
          <li><strong>Revenue increase:</strong> $400-550 monthly</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Most contractors see ROI within 6-9 months if they fully utilize FieldEdge's features. However, companies with simpler needs often achieve similar results with <a href="/hvac/crm/best-crm-for-small-hvac-companies">less expensive alternatives</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="alternatives">Cost-Effective FieldEdge Alternatives</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>If FieldEdge's pricing seems high, consider these alternatives that offer similar features at lower costs:</p>

        <h3>Best for Small HVAC Companies (1-5 technicians)</h3>
        <p><strong>Jobber:</strong> Starting at $49/user monthly with no setup fees. Includes scheduling, invoicing, customer management, and mobile apps. <a href="/hvac/crm/jobber-vs-servicetitan">90% of contractors find it sufficient</a> for basic operations.</p>

        <h3>Best for Growing Companies (5-15 technicians)</h3>
        <p><strong>Housecall Pro:</strong> $61/user monthly with advanced reporting included. Better customer communication features than FieldEdge and easier implementation.</p>

        <h3>Best for Large Operations (15+ technicians)</h3>
        <p><strong>ServiceTitan:</strong> More expensive but includes advanced features FieldEdge charges extra for. Better long-term value for companies planning rapid growth.</p>

        <p>See our detailed comparison in <a href="/hvac/crm/servicetitan-alternatives">ServiceTitan alternatives</a> for more options.</p>
      </div>

